      <section>
         <indexterm>UPS tuner</indexterm>
      </section>
      <section>
         <p>Connect the UPS Tuner to the service ports on either a
controller box or a display module (HMI) to perform critical functions,
e.g. firmware upgrades, UPS configuration, global report, logs analysis,
and LCM management.</p>
         <note type="note">Standard terminal applications
like Hyper Terminal or Tera Term cannot be used anymore to perform
any of the functions covered by the UPS Tuner. </note>
         <note type="note">You need a license to use the UPS Tuner software. See Service View
for details about obtaining a license or contact your local Schneider
Electric support.</note>
      </section>
